             American" style="cursor: pointer" valign="top"> </div><span class="phon">/ˈæksent/</span><span class="sep">,</span> <div class="sound audio_play_button pron-us icon-audio" data-src-mp3="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/media/english/us_pron/a/acc/accen/accent__us_2.mp3" data-src-ogg="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/media/english/us_pron_ogg/a/acc/accen/accent__us_2.ogg" title="accent pronunciation&#10;                    American" style="cursor: pointer" valign="top"> </div><span class="phon">/ˈæksənt/</span></div></span></div><a class="responsive_display_inline_on_smartphone link-right" href="#relatedentries">
